    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Mechanically, this chassis is beyond reproach: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. Compression and leak-down tests show factory-spec numbers across all cylinders. No oxidative fatigue or underbody corrosion. This is a turn-key collector-spec vehicle for the discerning purist.",
